* ADDRESS CONTROL TABLES - Version 4.4
*-----------------------------------------------------------
* Entries are a maximum of 16x16x16x1
* At least 2 spaces or <tab> between columns
* Comment lines begin with an asterisk (*)
* Blank lines are ignored
* THIS FILE MUST BE SAVED AS PLAIN TEXT 
*===========================================================
*   S T R E E T   S U F F I X   T A B L E   U S A
*===========================================================
* 1st Column = Common
* 2nd Column = Full Spelling
*              Avoid altering: "Street", "Avenue", "Road"
* 3rd Column = Abbreviation
* 4th Column = City Prefix Flag (Y/N)
*              When "Address_CSZ_Combined" is set to "True"
*              and a street suffix is already present, treat
*              this suffix as a part of the city name.
*              "1 MAIN ST 'FT' MYERS, FL"
*-----------------------------------------------------------

